# ProBuilder / Worldbuilding

## Source

- Package: **transitive** via `com.unity.feature.worldbuilding` (not a direct manifest line)
- Lock version: see `ProjectBootstrap/manifest.snapshot.json` → `transitive_notable.com.unity.probuilder`

## Policy

- **Greybox / blockout only** — ProBuilder meshes for layout and iteration
- **Production art**: bake/export to standard meshes or replace before ship; do not ship editable ProBuilder on runtime props without intent
- Keep ProBuilder objects under `--- LEVEL ---` or dedicated `Greybox/` subfolder

## MCP

- Activate group: **`probuilder`** → `manage_probuilder` (**experimental**)
- Verify mesh results in Scene view; prefer small, reviewable edits

## When not to use

- UI (UI Toolkit only)
- Final environment art — use DCC import pipeline instead
